    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>This Privacy Policy sets out how we, Say Media, Inc. (&ldquo;Say Media,&rdquo; &ldquo;we&rdquo; or &ldquo;us&rdquo;), collect, store and use information about you when you use or interact with our websites, <a href="https://www.saymedia.com">www.saymedia.com</a>, <a href="https://tempest.saymedia.com" target="_blank">tempest.saymedia.com</a>, and other websites and mobile services provided by Say Media (collectively the &ldquo;Network Websites&rdquo;) and where we otherwise obtain or collect information about you. This Privacy Policy is effective from May 25, 2018.</p>

    <h4>Contents</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="#id.816chifxdoem">Summary</a></li>
        <li><a href="#id.b7dubs9e6h5q">Our details</a></li>
