        <li><a href="#id.vliojpjoy589">How we collect or obtain information about you from third parties</a></li>
        <li><a href="#id.xo599s3euss">Disclosure and additional uses of your information</a></li>
        <li><a href="#id.9tckhtbw0onm">How long we retain your information</a></li>
        <li><a href="#id.yeuqrbjdc9c">How we secure your information</a></li>
